:5146,"adult":false,"title":"The In-Laws","video":false,"overview":"Right before his daughter's wedding, a mild-mannered foot doctor discovers that his new in-laws are international smugglers.","genre_ids":[28,35],"popularity":1.0853,"vote_count":301,"poster_path":"/uziAQLzimrP8eW3w37F8lo8CnD3.jpg","release_date":"2003-05-23","vote_average":5.635,"backdrop_path":"/2cT8Q75gYiseEuPOE55n3lmBpRk.jpg","original_title":"The In-Laws","original_language":"en"},{"id":5491,"adult":false,"title":"Battlefield Earth","video":false,"overview":"In the year 3000, man is no match for the Psychlos, a greedy, manipulative race of aliens on a quest for ultimate profit. Led by the powerful Terl, the Psychlos are stripping Earth clean of its natural resources, using the broken remnants of humanity as slaves. What is left of the human race has descended into a near primitive state. After being captured, it is up to Tyler to save mankind.","genre_ids":[878,28,12],"popularity":1.441,"vote_count":914,"poster_path":"/wXCRuBHdJ5aTFQdsuGJFXNdo79T.jpg","release_date":"2000-05-12","vote_average":3.323,"backdrop_path":"/hqJfW8G8FL28rckFHuCoKPecpG9.jpg","original_title":"Battlefield Earth","original_language":"en"},{"id":5353,"adult":false,"title":"The Hunting Party","video":false,"overview":"A young journalist, an experienced cameraman and a discredited reporter find their bold plan to capture Bosnia's top war criminal quickly spiraling out of control when a UN representative mistakes them for a CIA hit squad.","genre_ids":[28,12,53,18],"popularity":1.2499,"vote_count":348,"poster_path":"/kXUfQGa7BoW856hDYAFtZLtiAAQ.jpg","release_date":"2007-09-03","vote_average":6.497,"backdrop_path":"/k1dXZF6vyVgtmppyXWLZd9FmqmY.jpg","original_title":"The Hunting Party","original_language":"en"},{"id":5719,"adult":false,"title":"Mudhoney","video":false,"overview":"In this Depression-era tale, Calef is traveling from Michigan to California and stops in Spooner, Missouri, where Lute hires him for odd jobs. Calef gets involved with Lute's niece, Hannah. But she is married to Sidney, a wife-beating drunk who hopes to inherit his uncle-in-law's money. Sidney and an eccentric preacher plot against Calef, who finds it difficult to conceal his mysterious past and his growing affection for Sidney's wife.","genre_ids":[18,53],"popularity":0.3007,"vote_count":44,"poster_path":"/8iHie5qpBGrYpoC8ypN2m4PkPDe.jpg","release_date":"1965-05-25","vote_average":6,"backdrop_path":"/7HAxaIgeDHr2dGNmYiPwNJwM4BV.jpg","original_title":"Mudhoney","original_language":"en"},{"id":467438,"adult":false,"title":"King Spawn","video":false,"overview":"NYPD detective Twitch Williams investigates a series of grisly murder scenes, perpetrated by the mysterious supernatural vigilante Spawn.","genre_ids":[28,27],"popularity":1.7347,"vote_count":0,"poster_path":null,"release_date":"","vote_average":0,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"King Spawn","original_language":"en"},{"id":467306,"adult":false,"title":"Playing with Dolls: Havoc","video":false,"overview":"When serial killer Havoc escapes from his prison, there is no holding back. He descends upon unsuspecting lovers in their cabin get away. The world's most brutal killer is loose and his thirst for blood cannot be stopped.","genre_ids":[27,53],"popularity":0.7056,"vote_count":14,"poster_path":"/eQJ2Bg2p5HOf4lygC2TcRLf4quT.jpg","release_date":"2017-07-12","vote_average":4.7,"backdrop_path":"/6BumZcDN9zTrYihm4dVcaeoaq7J.jpg","original_title":"Playing with Dolls: Havoc","original_language":"en"},{"id":5527,"adult":false,"title":"A Killing Affair","video":false,"overview":"Peter Weller stars as Baton Morris, a drifter suspected of murder, in this crime drama. A widow (Kathy Baker) living in West Virginia takes in the man (Weller) whom she believes murdered her husband. As she spends more time with him, she begins to fall for him, but continues to question whether or not she can trust him. Directed by David Saperstein and based on a novel by Robert Houston, A Killing Affair features twists and turns up until the end.","genre_ids":[18,53,80],"popularity":0.2891,"vote_count":1,"poster_path":"/ws5Hz7Sh6GrN06fMeJeorqjRxP2.jpg","release_date":"1985-10-24","vote_average":6,"backdrop_path":"/j8n8so85LgbjlMCxl9CzhC4vIkE.jpg","original_title":"A Killing Affair","original_language":"en"},{"id":276175,"adult":false,"title":"The Treasure of Moctezuma","video":false,"overview":"Santo and Jorge Rivero team-up to stop an international syndicate from stealing Mexico's greatest treasure.","genre_ids":[28],"popularity":0.2973,"vote_count":10,"poster_path":"/3ZOEq7FeIDsFB3NpMG0BX8ZzKBe.jpg","release_date":"1968-07-04","vote_average":5.2,"backdrop_path":"/ta0WSKsmm70SztVY6zFIk0FNXQq.jpg","original_title":"El tesoro de Moctezuma","original_language":"es"},{"id":658408,"adult":false,"title":"Rafadan Tayfa: Göbeklitepe","video":false,"overview":"The discovery of Göbeklitepe and the subsequent excavations caused great excitement around the world. During the days when all eyes were on Göbeklitepe, Akın received a mysterious package from his friend Veysi in Şanlıurfa. While Akın couldn't make sense of the copper tray that came out of the package, a phone call from Veysi made the situation even more complicated. In a state of panic, Veysi said that someone was after him, but the call was cut off.","genre_ids":[16,878,12,10751],"popularity":0.3221,"vote_count":8,"poster_path":"/o9tgtWWJm2WRJT0E9Z4SEmvFuBL.jpg","release_date":"2019-12-27","vote_average":5.4,"backdrop_path":"/tD5ZeGLsfiWQf0H9fLyBAKWXRgD.jpg","original_title":"Rafadan Tayfa: Göbeklitepe","original_language":"tr"},{"id":5549,"adult":false,"title":"RoboCop 2","video":false,"overview":"After a successful deployment of the RoboCop Law Enforcement unit, OCP sees its goal of urban pacification come closer and closer, but as this develops, a new narcotic known as \"Nuke\" invades the streets led by God-delirious leader Cane. As this menace grows, it may prove to be too much for Murphy to handle. OCP tries to replicate the success of the first unit, but ends up with failed prototypes with suicidal issues... until Dr. Faxx, a scientist straying away from OCP's path, uses Cane as the new subject for the RoboCop 2 project, a living God.","genre_ids":[28,12,80,878,53],"popularity":3.2385,"vote_count":2068,"poster_path":"/nhqBxhOJXUJeFsyLxTFkctH9H5F.jpg","release_date":"1990-06-22","vote_average":6.029,"backdrop_path":"/cT0YCYCtAQC8wi56VWK1JRGgk3a.jpg","original_title":"RoboCop 2","original_language":"en"},{"id":5550,"adult":false,"title":"RoboCop 3","video":false,"overview":"The mega corporation Omni Consumer Products is still bent on creating their pet project, Delta City, to replace the rotting city of Detroit. Unfortunately, the inhabitants of the area have no intention of abandoning their homes simply for desires of the company. To this end, OCP have decided to force them to leave by employing a ruthless mercenary army to attack and harass them. An underground resistance begins and in this fight, RoboCop must decide where his loyalties lie.","genre_ids":[28,12,80,878,53],"popularity":3.2456,"vote_count":1408,"poster_path":"/ppLSSwCuC5ERRWbu9H3R8SPL9AM.jpg","release_date":"1993-01-21","vote_average":4.9,"backdrop_path":"/5IevASZ9agBjA8SDDZLbBgFDbsP.jpg","original_title":"RoboCop 3","original_language":"en"},{"id":1256654,"adult":false,"title":"Helix","video":false,"overview":"As a bodyguard at the BKA, Helen Schilling is responsible for the security of the controversial Minister of Economics and Environment Richard Bauer at a press event. When Bauer has a seizure in front of the journalists, it quickly becomes clear: the minister has been the victim of a targeted attack. In the course of the investigation, Helen becomes involved in a highly explosive plot, behind which a war for the dominance of future genetic research and its ethical limits is unfolding.","genre_ids":[53,80,10770],"popularity":3.1237,"vote_count":5,"poster_path":"/vRR5bW5eIateOyUKxxeVlAWJC0y.jpg","release_date":"2024-11-01","vote_average":6,"backdrop_path":"/2oPQ54YYZQJNAkb3I3aIYUEyFg.jpg","original_title":"Helix","original_language":"de"},{"id":278154,"adult":false,"title":"Ice Age: Collision Course","video":false,"overview":"Set after the events of Continental Drift, Scrat's epic pursuit of his elusive acorn catapults him outside of Earth, where he accidentally sets off a series of cosmic events that transform and threaten the planet. To save themselves from peril, Manny, Sid, Diego, and the rest of the herd leave their home and embark on a quest full of thrills and spills, highs and lows, laughter and adventure while traveling to exotic new lands and locations.","genre_ids":[12,16,10751,35,878],"popularity":5.3538,"vote_count":4813,"poster_path":"/dWyaaP1dmW5peBvgiVaugdRuyYD.jpg","release_date":"2016-06-23","vote_average":6.1,"backdrop_path":"/wQoe0j7ZDk7LWexC0XhwkK4brIb.jpg","original_title":"Ice Age: Collision Course","original_language":"en"},{"id":9080,"adult":false,"title":"Spies Like Us","video":false,"overview":"Two bumbling government employees think they are U.S. spies, only to discover that they are actually decoys for nuclear war.","genre_ids":[35,12],"popularity":2.6982,"vote_count":686,"poster_path":"/s0Sx8nd9Irq0aCPbsN78s0DYVlG.jpg","release_date":"1985-12-06","vote_average":6.182,"backdrop_path":"/9RJGN6CaCFOzs9H1yie2aPxLUoX.jpg","original_title":"Spies Like Us","original_language":"en"},{"id":9086,"adult":false,"title":"Young Guns II","video":false,"overview":"Three of the original five \"young guns\" — Billy the Kid, Jose Chavez y Chavez, and Doc Scurlock — return in Young Guns, Part 2, which is the story of Billy the Kid and his race to safety in Old Mexico while being trailed by a group of government agents led by Pat Garrett.","genre_ids":[37,12],"popularity":1.5366,"vote_count":579,"poster_path":"/7kMjla98srGHlFzAEmoGRcr6GN1.jpg","release_date":"1990-08-01","vote_average":6.503,"backdrop_path":"/sQNPWOTzl5kkZTW5ogSu0uSnre